      "role": "user",
      "content": "wow that is a huge difference. a thousand bucks difference in interest alone? it feels like almost all that money is just disappearing for the first few years without helping me own the house more. it feels like the interest is just eating up my money before i even see any progress. how do people even deal with that feeling?",
